data.name: ChartSeriesAddress
desc: This structure describes a single data row, specified by its name and a sequence of data points.
The cell addresses are in the format of the application that contains this chart.

items.name: DataRangeAddress
lines: contains the cell range address of the data for this series.

items.name: DomainRangeAddresses
lines: contains cell addresses for each domain of this series.
For XY (scatter) diagrams at least one series has a domain. Most of the other chart types use an empty sequence here.
